Teamlock Chrome Extension.
Teamlock is an Enterprise Secret Manger designed for enteprises.

Store your secrets in one workspace per team, then grant access to your collaborators.
All your collaborators will be able to retreive sensitive informations they need to properly work, without sharing a common password.
